Caddyfile

# NOTE: uv.lock is intentionally NOT ignored — the slim Dockerfile does
# `COPY pyproject.toml uv.lock` + `uv sync --frozen`. The old "Mac CUDA"
# warning is obsolete: torch/CUDA were dropped, the lockfile is lean and
# resolves correct Linux wheels.
